Being the bored person I am I said â€œwhy not?â€ And then I got asked for my email. â€œWhy notâ€ as soon as I verified my phone number and email I kept getting calls THREATENING to kill me if I donâ€™t vote for trump. And I got spam emails. I will copy them here â€œ Dear,                 Thanks for downloading my app. Now revote for me. Or I will come to your house and dance on your kitchen table like a anorexic Cheeto puff.â€ I said â€œ :0â€ but again thought nothing of it as I continued to get spam calls and emails I heard a ring on my doorbell. Not even a second later THE Donald j trump BURST through my door wearing an ill-fitting Cheeto puff costume and started dancing on my kitchen table. Luckily John cena came through my wall and said â€œare you sure about that?â€ And he killed Donald trump with my butterknife. Overall terrible experience and customer service. -100000/10 would not recommend.
